{"tid":1334514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［721］如果爆炸品單野流唔流都好 都要堅持不割蓆","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:24:44.000Z","uid":269052,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7d23269e452357c6e04a818dda8bbcd88c499854","tid":1334514,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"先講我既諗法，荃灣單野，有哂香港民族陣線既T-Shirt，9成9係做9梁頌恆<br />\n<br />\n一黎梁頌恆重堅持港獨，二黎梁頌恆同郭文貴單野鬧到熱烘烘<br />\n<br />\n獻世派可以借哩單野話美國資助香港港獨份子，外國勢力同顏色革命兩個論述就更有力<br />\n<br />\n問題係，哩單新聞正正<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">試緊各位既底線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n港共一定係度諗，班人話不割蓆，但總會有個底線係大家割之而後快<br />\n<br />\n預料港共會繼續做新聞，不斷逼我地割蓆<br />\n<br />\n哩個時候，我地底線要清楚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論如何 絕不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721 明天見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2otWj1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2otWj1t.png&h=ea449eda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"324f13699d288cf8c7fb7ad0996657f8202adacf","tid":1334514,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78710deb3b3002a723995a00e695e5d45768bb36","tid":1334514,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c